import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import tensorflow as tf
def kmeansCluster(X,numClusters):
    get_inputs=lambda: tf.train.limit_epochs(tf.convert_to_tensor(X.as_matrix(), dtype=tf.float32), num_epochs=1)
    cluster = tf.contrib.factorization.KMeansClustering(num_clusters=numClusters,use_mini_batch=False)
    cluster.train(input_fn=get_inputs,steps=2000)
    y_pred=cluster.predict_cluster_index(input_fn=get_inputs)
    y_pred=np.asarray(list(y_pred))
    return y_pred

k=2000
points=pd.read_csv("data/source_data.csv",usecols=[14,15,16,17,18])

y= kmeansCluster(points,k)
print(y)
